## This folder contains the files required for the creation and installation of this repo's package

sub folders:

./bin              .deb file and install_package.sh used to install the binary on the user machine
./source           source files that are required for creating and updating the package
./create_package.sh  a script that can be used to create a package


## create or update the package

 $ cd /your/dir/to/package/bin
 $ create_package.sh 
 
## installation

 $ cd /your/dir/to/package/bin
 $ sudo ./install_package.sh


